    • Field Detail

      • name

        protected java.lang.String name
        The name (or tag) of the token. This is the key that is used in the various map attributes of classes that extend UmlToken. Example: UmlClass.attributes.

      • content

        protected java.lang.String content
        The String content of the class, as declared by the .ucd file that was parsed. This text, however, is formated to be easier to parse so it contains some character that is not proper for display.
